{"title":"西财摄记 | Round and round","uid":"1fc4783e0d5bd21de1c0f61ddfb36851","slug":"推文16","date":"2021-11-22T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:49:19.924Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文16.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004525721.png","content":"<p>“It’s beautiful life, </p>\n<p> Beautiful day.”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004514592.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004514592\"></p>\n<p>再一次迎来属于你我的季节</p>\n<p>你还会记得吗</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004521108.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004521108\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004525721.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004525721\"></p>\n<p>听说人会经历四次人生</p>\n<p>可能的话，希望这是第一生</p>\n<p>那样的话</p>\n<p>第二生，第三生，还有最后一生</p>\n<p>都能与你相遇</p>\n<p> <img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004545771.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004545771\"></p>\n<p>一召唤就会有回应的声音</p>\n<p>在同一时间看过同一事物的回忆</p>\n<p>彼此首次漫步的瞬间</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004556184.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004556184\"></p>\n<p>想起谁了吗</p>\n<p>对 就是那个人</p>\n<p>那个温柔的存在</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004606115.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004606115\"></p>\n<p>长日欣喜，四季与你</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004615561.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004615561\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004619367.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004619367\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004623368.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004623368\"></p>\n<p>自从认识他之后，</p>\n<p>她就再没有看过星星</p>\n<p>看星星做什么</p>\n<p>看他的眼睛就够了</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004634870.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004634870\"></p>\n<p>只记住那些幸福而闪耀的日子</p>\n<p>忘记了所有悲伤又痛苦的时刻</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004648356.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004648356\"></p>\n<p>记住  一定要记住</p>\n<p>我是那个人的新娘</p>\n<p> <img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304004659390.png\" alt=\"image-20220304004659390\"></p>\n<p>一起走过的所有路，</p>\n<p>一起看过的所有风景，</p>\n<p>羞涩或心动地提出和回答的 所有问题和答案，</p>\n<p>每一个瞬间的他，</p>\n<p>她都喜欢</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><pre><code>                                                 摄影师碎碎念 \n</code></pre>\n<p>​    连绵数日的阴雨突然失去踪影，久违的阳光照上阳台，约嘉欣摄影的念头一下子在岑寂的光阴中跃起，那不如就约到今天吧！摄影轻松消除了我们初见的陌生感，我看她在阳光下蹁跹和表现，从发梢舞至夕阳最后一缕。</p>\n<p>​    你要相信，地球在转的，不会一直在雨季。</p>\n<p>​                                                下个小雪，期待再见</p></blockquote>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p>摄影 | 杨康</p>\n<p>模特 | 孙嘉欣</p>\n<p>策划 | 刘雨童 田思妮</p>\n<p>排版 | 杜钰阳</p>\n\n</details>\n","text":"“It’s beautiful life, Beautiful day.” 再一次迎来属于你我的季节 你还会记得吗 听说人会经历四次人生 可能的话，希望这是第一生 那样的话 第二生，第三生，还有最后一生 都能与你相遇 一召唤就会有回应的声音 在同一时间看过同一事物的回忆 彼此首次...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":631,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":9,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"秋","slug":"秋","count":5,"path":"api/tags/秋.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"西财烟火觅食记 | 秋","uid":"a92b5d34203faa6d9f41960d55b5dfe1","slug":"推文17","date":"2021-12-08T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:56:33.077Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文17.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005020466.png","text":" 人间忽晚，山河已秋。 踩着满地银杏，走进西财的秋。 「秋天来了」的意思是 街边卖糖炒栗子的小店开始排起长队 月色一日比一日清素 雨声从热闹变得沉寂 人们个个神色清醒，心思澄净 日子忽然缓慢而悠长 有趣的人生，一半是山川湖海，一半是烟